{
  "id": 50,
  "nameSimple": "Qaf",
  "nameArabic": "ق",
  "versesCount": 45,
  "revelationPlace": "makkah",
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": 4631,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "verseKey": "50:1",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 454,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": " قٓ ۚ وَٱلْقُرْءَانِ ٱلْمَجِيدِ",
      "pageNumber": 518,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100203,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Qāf.<sup foot_note=229758>1</sup> By the honored Qur’ān...<sup foot_note=229759>2</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751344,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "嘎弗。以尊严的《古兰经》盟誓。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4632,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "verseKey": "50:2",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 454,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "بَلْ عَجِبُوٓا۟ أَن جَآءَهُم مُّنذِرٌ مِّنْهُمْ فَقَالَ ٱلْكَـٰفِرُونَ هَـٰذَا شَىْءٌ عَجِيبٌ",
      "pageNumber": 518,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100214,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "But they wonder that there has come to them a warner from among themselves, and the disbelievers say, \"This is an amazing thing.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751345,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "难道他们因同族的警告者来临他们而惊讶吗？不信道的人们说：“这是奇事！",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4633,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "verseKey": "50:3",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 454,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "أَءِذَا مِتْنَا وَكُنَّا تُرَابًا ۖ ذَٰلِكَ رَجْعٌۢ بَعِيدٌ",
      "pageNumber": 518,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100225,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "When we have died and have become dust, [we will return to life]? That is a distant [i.e., unlikely] return.\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751346,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "难道我们既死之后，已变成尘土，还要还原吗？那太不近情理了。”",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4634,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "verseKey": "50:4",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 454,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "قَدْ عَلِمْنَا مَا تَنقُصُ ٱلْأَرْضُ مِنْهُمْ ۖ وَعِندَنَا كِتَـٰبٌ حَفِيظٌۢ",
      "pageNumber": 518,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100236,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "We know what the earth diminishes [i.e., consumes] of them, and with Us is a retaining record.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751347,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我确已知道大地对于他们的剥蚀，我这里有一本被保护的天经。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4635,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "verseKey": "50:5",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 454,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "بَلْ كَذَّبُوا۟ بِٱلْحَقِّ لَمَّا جَآءَهُمْ فَهُمْ فِىٓ أَمْرٍ مَّرِيجٍ",
      "pageNumber": 518,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100243,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "But they denied the truth when it came to them, so they are in a confused condition.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751348,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他们否认已降示他们的真理，所以他们陷于混乱的状态中。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4636,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "verseKey": "50:6",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 454,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "أَفَلَمْ يَنظُرُوٓا۟ إِلَى ٱلسَّمَآءِ فَوْقَهُمْ كَيْفَ بَنَيْنَـٰهَا وَزَيَّنَّـٰهَا وَمَا لَهَا مِن فُرُوجٍ",
      "pageNumber": 518,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100244,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Have they not looked at the heaven above them - how We structured it and adorned it and [how] it has no rifts?",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751349,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "难道他们没有仰视天体吗？我是怎样建造它，点缀它，使它没有缺陷的？",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4637,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "verseKey": "50:7",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 454,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَٱلْأَرْضَ مَدَدْنَـٰهَا وَأَلْقَيْنَا فِيهَا رَوَٰسِىَ وَأَنۢبَتْنَا فِيهَا مِن كُلِّ زَوْجٍۭ بَهِيجٍ",
      "pageNumber": 518,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100245,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And the earth - We spread it out and cast therein firmly set mountains and made grow therein [something] of every beautiful kind,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751350,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我曾展开大地，并将许多山岳投在上面，还使各种美丽的植物生长出来，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4638,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "verseKey": "50:8",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 454,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "تَبْصِرَةً وَذِكْرَىٰ لِكُلِّ عَبْدٍ مُّنِيبٍ",
      "pageNumber": 518,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100246,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Giving insight and a reminder for every servant who turns [to Allāh].",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751351,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "为的是启发和教诲每个归依的仆人。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4639,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "verseKey": "50:9",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 454,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَنَزَّلْنَا مِنَ ٱلسَّمَآءِ مَآءً مُّبَـٰرَكًا فَأَنۢبَتْنَا بِهِۦ جَنَّـٰتٍ وَحَبَّ ٱلْحَصِيدِ",
      "pageNumber": 518,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100247,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And We have sent down blessed rain from the sky and made grow thereby gardens and grain from the harvest",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751352,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我从天上降下吉祥的雨水，就借它而生长出许多果树和五谷，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4640,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "verseKey": "50:10",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 454,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَٱلنَّخْلَ بَاسِقَـٰتٍ لَّهَا طَلْعٌ نَّضِيدٌ",
      "pageNumber": 518,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100204,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And lofty palm trees having fruit arranged in layers -",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751353,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "并生长扶疏的海枣树，它有累累的果实，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4641,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "verseKey": "50:11",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 454,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "رِّزْقًا لِّلْعِبَادِ ۖ وَأَحْيَيْنَا بِهِۦ بَلْدَةً مَّيْتًا ۚ كَذَٰلِكَ ٱلْخُرُوجُ",
      "pageNumber": 518,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100205,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "As provision for the servants, and We have given life thereby to a dead land. Thus is the emergence [i.e., resurrection].",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751354,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "用作众仆的给养。我借雨水而使已死的地方复活。死人的复活也是这样的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4642,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "verseKey": "50:12",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 454,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "كَذَّبَتْ قَبْلَهُمْ قَوْمُ نُوحٍ وَأَصْحَـٰبُ ٱلرَّسِّ وَثَمُودُ",
      "pageNumber": 518,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100206,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "The people of Noah denied before them,<sup foot_note=229762>1</sup> and the companions of the well<sup foot_note=229763>2</sup> and Thamūd",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751355,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "在他们之前否认使者的人，有努哈的宗族、兰斯的居民、赛莫德人、",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4643,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "verseKey": "50:13",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 454,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَعَادٌ وَفِرْعَوْنُ وَإِخْوَٰنُ لُوطٍ",
      "pageNumber": 518,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100207,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And ʿAad and Pharaoh and the brothers [i.e., people] of Lot",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751356,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "阿德人、法老、鲁特的同胞、",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4644,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "verseKey": "50:14",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 454,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَأَصْحَـٰبُ ٱلْأَيْكَةِ وَقَوْمُ تُبَّعٍ ۚ كُلٌّ كَذَّبَ ٱلرُّسُلَ فَحَقَّ وَعِيدِ",
      "pageNumber": 518,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100208,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And the companions of the thicket and the people of Tubbaʿ. All denied the messengers, so My threat was justly fulfilled.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751357,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "丛林的居民和图白的百姓，统统都否认过使者，故我所警告的刑罚，是必然降临的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4645,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "verseKey": "50:15",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 454,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "أَفَعَيِينَا بِٱلْخَلْقِ ٱلْأَوَّلِ ۚ بَلْ هُمْ فِى لَبْسٍ مِّنْ خَلْقٍ جَدِيدٍ",
      "pageNumber": 518,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100209,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Did We fail in the first creation? But they are in confusion over a new creation.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751358,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我曾因创造而疲倦吗？不然，他们对于再造，是在疑惑中的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4646,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "verseKey": "50:16",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 455,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَلَقَدْ خَلَقْنَا ٱلْإِنسَـٰنَ وَنَعْلَمُ مَا تُوَسْوِسُ بِهِۦ نَفْسُهُۥ ۖ وَنَحْنُ أَقْرَبُ إِلَيْهِ مِنْ حَبْلِ ٱلْوَرِيدِ",
      "pageNumber": 519,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100210,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And We have already created man and know what his soul whispers to him, and We are closer<sup foot_note=229764>1</sup> to him than [his] jugular vein.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751359,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我确已创造人，我知道他心中的妄想；我比他的命脉还近于他。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4647,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "verseKey": "50:17",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 455,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِذْ يَتَلَقَّى ٱلْمُتَلَقِّيَانِ عَنِ ٱلْيَمِينِ وَعَنِ ٱلشِّمَالِ قَعِيدٌ",
      "pageNumber": 519,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100211,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "When the two receivers [i.e., recording angels] receive,<sup foot_note=229765>1</sup> seated on the right and on the left.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751360,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "当坐在右边和左边的两个记录的天使记录各人的言行的时候，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4648,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "verseKey": "50:18",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 455,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "مَّا يَلْفِظُ مِن قَوْلٍ إِلَّا لَدَيْهِ رَقِيبٌ عَتِيدٌ",
      "pageNumber": 519,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100212,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "He [i.e., man] utters no word except that with him is an observer prepared [to record].",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751361,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他每说一句话，他面前都有天使当场监察。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4649,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "verseKey": "50:19",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 455,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَجَآءَتْ سَكْرَةُ ٱلْمَوْتِ بِٱلْحَقِّ ۖ ذَٰلِكَ مَا كُنتَ مِنْهُ تَحِيدُ",
      "pageNumber": 519,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100213,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And the intoxication of death will bring the truth; that is what you were trying to avoid.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751362,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "临死的昏迷，将昭示真理。这是你一向所逃避的",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4650,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "verseKey": "50:20",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 455,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَنُفِخَ فِى ٱلصُّورِ ۚ ذَٰلِكَ يَوْمُ ٱلْوَعِيدِ",
      "pageNumber": 519,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100215,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And the Horn will be blown. That is the Day of [carrying out] the threat.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751363,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "号角将吹响，那是警告实现之日。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4651,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "verseKey": "50:21",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 455,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَجَآءَتْ كُلُّ نَفْسٍ مَّعَهَا سَآئِقٌ وَشَهِيدٌ",
      "pageNumber": 519,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100216,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And every soul will come, with it a driver and a witness.<sup foot_note=229766>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751364,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "每个人都要到来，驱逐的天使和见证的天使，将与他同行。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4652,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "verseKey": "50:22",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 455,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "لَّقَدْ كُنتَ فِى غَفْلَةٍ مِّنْ هَـٰذَا فَكَشَفْنَا عَنكَ غِطَآءَكَ فَبَصَرُكَ ٱلْيَوْمَ حَدِيدٌ",
      "pageNumber": 519,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100217,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "[It will be said], \"You were certainly in unmindfulness of this, and We have removed from you your cover,<sup foot_note=229767>1</sup> so your sight, this Day, is sharp.\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751365,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "你确疏忽此事，现在我已揭开你的蒙蔽，所以你今日的眼光是锐利的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4653,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "verseKey": "50:23",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 455,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَقَالَ قَرِينُهُۥ هَـٰذَا مَا لَدَىَّ عَتِيدٌ",
      "pageNumber": 519,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100218,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And his companion, [the angel], will say, \"This [record] is what is with me, prepared.\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751366,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他的伙伴将说：“这在我面前是现成的。”",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4654,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "verseKey": "50:24",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 455,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "أَلْقِيَا فِى جَهَنَّمَ كُلَّ كَفَّارٍ عَنِيدٍ",
      "pageNumber": 519,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100219,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "[Allāh will say], \"Throw into Hell every obstinate disbeliever,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751367,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "你俩所应当投入火狱的，是每个孤负者、顽固者、",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4655,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "verseKey": "50:25",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 455,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "مَّنَّاعٍ لِّلْخَيْرِ مُعْتَدٍ مُّرِيبٍ",
      "pageNumber": 519,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100220,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Preventer of good, aggressor, and doubter,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751368,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "悭吝者、过分者、怀疑者、",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4656,
      "verseNumber": 26,
      "verseKey": "50:26",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 207,
      "rukuNumber": 455,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "ٱلَّذِى جَعَلَ مَعَ ٱللَّهِ إِلَـٰهًا ءَاخَرَ فَأَلْقِيَاهُ فِى ٱلْعَذَابِ ٱلشَّدِيدِ",
      "pageNumber": 519,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100221,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Who made [as equal] with Allāh another deity; then throw him into the severe punishment.\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751369,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "以别的神灵与安拉同受崇拜者；你俩将他投入严厉的刑罚吧！",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4657,
      "verseNumber": 27,
      "verseKey": "50:27",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 208,
      "rukuNumber": 455,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "۞ قَالَ قَرِينُهُۥ رَبَّنَا مَآ أَطْغَيْتُهُۥ وَلَـٰكِن كَانَ فِى ضَلَـٰلٍۭ بَعِيدٍ",
      "pageNumber": 519,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100222,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "His [devil] companion will say, \"Our Lord, I did not make him transgress, but he [himself] was in extreme error.\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751370,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他的伙伴将说：“我的主啊！我没有使他放荡，但他自陷于不近情理的迷误中。”",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4658,
      "verseNumber": 28,
      "verseKey": "50:28",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 208,
      "rukuNumber": 455,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "قَالَ لَا تَخْتَصِمُوا۟ لَدَىَّ وَقَدْ قَدَّمْتُ إِلَيْكُم بِٱلْوَعِيدِ",
      "pageNumber": 519,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100223,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "[Allāh] will say, \"Do not dispute before Me, while I had already presented to you the threat [i.e., warning].",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751371,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "主将说：“你们不要在我面前争论，我确已预先警告你们了。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4659,
      "verseNumber": 29,
      "verseKey": "50:29",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 208,
      "rukuNumber": 455,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "مَا يُبَدَّلُ ٱلْقَوْلُ لَدَىَّ وَمَآ أَنَا۠ بِظَلَّـٰمٍ لِّلْعَبِيدِ",
      "pageNumber": 519,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100224,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "The word [i.e., decree] will not be changed with Me, and never will I be unjust to the servants.\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751372,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我的判词，是不可变更的，我绝不是亏枉众仆的。”",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4660,
      "verseNumber": 30,
      "verseKey": "50:30",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 208,
      "rukuNumber": 456,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "يَوْمَ نَقُولُ لِجَهَنَّمَ هَلِ ٱمْتَلَأْتِ وَتَقُولُ هَلْ مِن مَّزِيدٍ",
      "pageNumber": 519,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100226,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "On the Day We will say to Hell, \"Have you been filled?\" and it will say, \"Are there some more,\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751373,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "在那日，我将对火狱说：“你已填满了吗？”它将说：“还有增加的吗？",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4661,
      "verseNumber": 31,
      "verseKey": "50:31",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 208,
      "rukuNumber": 456,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَأُزْلِفَتِ ٱلْجَنَّةُ لِلْمُتَّقِينَ غَيْرَ بَعِيدٍ",
      "pageNumber": 519,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100227,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And Paradise will be brought near to the righteous, not far,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751374,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "乐园将被移到敬畏者的附近，离得不远。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4662,
      "verseNumber": 32,
      "verseKey": "50:32",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 208,
      "rukuNumber": 456,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "هَـٰذَا مَا تُوعَدُونَ لِكُلِّ أَوَّابٍ حَفِيظٍ",
      "pageNumber": 519,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100228,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "[It will be said], \"This is what you were promised - for every returner [to Allāh] and keeper [of His covenant].",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751375,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "这是你们所被应许的，这是赏赐每个归依的守礼者的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4663,
      "verseNumber": 33,
      "verseKey": "50:33",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 208,
      "rukuNumber": 456,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "مَّنْ خَشِىَ ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنَ بِٱلْغَيْبِ وَجَآءَ بِقَلْبٍ مُّنِيبٍ",
      "pageNumber": 519,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100229,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Who feared the Most Merciful in the unseen and came with a heart returning [in repentance].",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751376,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "秘密敬畏至仁主，且带归依的心而来者，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4664,
      "verseNumber": 34,
      "verseKey": "50:34",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 208,
      "rukuNumber": 456,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "ٱدْخُلُوهَا بِسَلَـٰمٍ ۖ ذَٰلِكَ يَوْمُ ٱلْخُلُودِ",
      "pageNumber": 519,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100230,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Enter it in peace. This is the Day of Eternity.\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751377,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "你们平安地进入乐园吧！这是永居开始之日。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4665,
      "verseNumber": 35,
      "verseKey": "50:35",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 208,
      "rukuNumber": 456,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "لَهُم مَّا يَشَآءُونَ فِيهَا وَلَدَيْنَا مَزِيدٌ",
      "pageNumber": 519,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100231,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "They will have whatever they wish therein, and with Us is more.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751378,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他们在乐园里，将有他们意欲的；而且我在那里还有加赐。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4666,
      "verseNumber": 36,
      "verseKey": "50:36",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 208,
      "rukuNumber": 456,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَكَمْ أَهْلَكْنَا قَبْلَهُم مِّن قَرْنٍ هُمْ أَشَدُّ مِنْهُم بَطْشًا فَنَقَّبُوا۟ فِى ٱلْبِلَـٰدِ هَلْ مِن مَّحِيصٍ",
      "pageNumber": 520,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100232,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And how many a generation before them did We destroy who were greater than them in [striking] power and had explored throughout the lands. Is there any place of escape?",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751379,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "在他们之前，我毁灭了许多比他们更强悍的世代！他们曾在各地旅行，难道有什么避死的地方吗？",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4667,
      "verseNumber": 37,
      "verseKey": "50:37",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 208,
      "rukuNumber": 456,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّ فِى ذَٰلِكَ لَذِكْرَىٰ لِمَن كَانَ لَهُۥ قَلْبٌ أَوْ أَلْقَى ٱلسَّمْعَ وَهُوَ شَهِيدٌ",
      "pageNumber": 520,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100233,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed in that is a reminder for whoever has a heart or who listens while he is present [in mind].",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751380,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "对于有心灵者，或专心静听者，此中确有一种教训。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4668,
      "verseNumber": 38,
      "verseKey": "50:38",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 208,
      "rukuNumber": 456,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَلَقَدْ خَلَقْنَا ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضَ وَمَا بَيْنَهُمَا فِى سِتَّةِ أَيَّامٍ وَمَا مَسَّنَا مِن لُّغُوبٍ",
      "pageNumber": 520,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100234,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And We did certainly create the heavens and earth and what is between them in six days, and there touched Us no weariness.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751381,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我在六日内确已创造了天地万物，我没有感觉一点疲倦。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4669,
      "verseNumber": 39,
      "verseKey": "50:39",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 208,
      "rukuNumber": 456,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَٱصْبِرْ عَلَىٰ مَا يَقُولُونَ وَسَبِّحْ بِحَمْدِ رَبِّكَ قَبْلَ طُلُوعِ ٱلشَّمْسِ وَقَبْلَ ٱلْغُرُوبِ",
      "pageNumber": 520,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100235,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "So be patient, [O Muḥammad], over what they say and exalt [Allāh] with praise of your Lord before the rising of the sun and before its setting,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751382,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "故你应当忍受他们所说的谰言。在日出日落之前，你应当赞颂你的主；",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4670,
      "verseNumber": 40,
      "verseKey": "50:40",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 208,
      "rukuNumber": 456,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَمِنَ ٱلَّيْلِ فَسَبِّحْهُ وَأَدْبَـٰرَ ٱلسُّجُودِ",
      "pageNumber": 520,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100237,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And [in part] of the night exalt Him and after prostration [i.e., prayer].",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751383,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "在夜间和叩头后，你应当赞颂他。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4671,
      "verseNumber": 41,
      "verseKey": "50:41",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 208,
      "rukuNumber": 456,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَٱسْتَمِعْ يَوْمَ يُنَادِ ٱلْمُنَادِ مِن مَّكَانٍ قَرِيبٍ",
      "pageNumber": 520,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100238,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And listen on the Day when the Caller<sup foot_note=229770>1</sup> will call out from a place that is near -",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751384,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "你应当倾听，在喊叫者从近处喊叫之日，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4672,
      "verseNumber": 42,
      "verseKey": "50:42",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 208,
      "rukuNumber": 456,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "يَوْمَ يَسْمَعُونَ ٱلصَّيْحَةَ بِٱلْحَقِّ ۚ ذَٰلِكَ يَوْمُ ٱلْخُرُوجِ",
      "pageNumber": 520,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100239,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "The Day they will hear the blast [of the Horn] in truth. That is the Day of Emergence [from the graves].",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751385,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "在他们听见包含真理的呐喊之日，那是从坟中出来之日。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4673,
      "verseNumber": 43,
      "verseKey": "50:43",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 208,
      "rukuNumber": 456,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّا نَحْنُ نُحْىِۦ وَنُمِيتُ وَإِلَيْنَا ٱلْمَصِيرُ",
      "pageNumber": 520,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100240,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, it is We who give life and cause death, and to Us is the destination",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751386,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我确是使人生、使人死的，我确是最后的归宿。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4674,
      "verseNumber": 44,
      "verseKey": "50:44",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 208,
      "rukuNumber": 456,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "يَوْمَ تَشَقَّقُ ٱلْأَرْضُ عَنْهُمْ سِرَاعًا ۚ ذَٰلِكَ حَشْرٌ عَلَيْنَا يَسِيرٌ",
      "pageNumber": 520,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100241,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "On the Day the earth breaks away from them [and they emerge] rapidly; that is a gathering easy for Us.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751387,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "在大地破裂而他们迅速走出坟墓之日，那集合的事对于我是容易的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4675,
      "verseNumber": 45,
      "verseKey": "50:45",
      "hizbNumber": 52,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 208,
      "rukuNumber": 456,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "نَّحْنُ أَعْلَمُ بِمَا يَقُولُونَ ۖ وَمَآ أَنتَ عَلَيْهِم بِجَبَّارٍ ۖ فَذَكِّرْ بِٱلْقُرْءَانِ مَن يَخَافُ وَعِيدِ",
      "pageNumber": 520,
      "juzNumber": 26,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 100242,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "We are most knowing of what they say, and you are not over them a tyrant.<sup foot_note=229771>1</sup> But remind by the Qur’ān whoever fears My threat.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 751388,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我全知他们所说的谰言，你不能强制他们，故你应当以《古兰经》教诲畏惧我的警告的人们。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}